<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.RenderPluginEnumerator.Destructor" Title="Destructor method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.RenderPluginEnumerator">RenderPluginEnumerator</PageRef> ->
    Destructor
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>RenderPluginEnumerator</TypeRef> destructor clears all loaded plugins and releases the module handles owned by the enumerator.
    </Paragraph>
    <Note Type="Warning">
      <Paragraph>
        Destroying the enumerator can unload plugin libraries. Ensure that objects created by those plugins have already been destroyed, or keep an independent module handle alive.
      </Paragraph>
    </Note>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[~RenderPluginEnumerator();]]></Code>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="See also">
    <PageRefList>
      <PageRefListEntry PageName="cobalt.graphics.RenderPluginEnumerator.ClearAllPlugins">RenderPluginEnumerator.ClearAllPlugins</PageRefListEntry>
    </PageRefList>
  </Section>
</XMLDocContent>
